description:
Handle errors on frontend, there should be some indicatior that error occured and page cannot be displayed when Graphql returns errors, and example of errored response:

{errors: [,…], data: {auditLogs: {totalCount: 36,…}}}
data
: 
{auditLogs: {totalCount: 36,…}}
errors
: 
[,…]
0
: 
{message: "String cannot represent value: { isActive: true }", locations: [{line: 23, column: 19}],…}
1
: 
{message: "String cannot represent value: { isActive: false }", locations: [{line: 24, column: 19}],…}
2
: 
{message: "String cannot represent value: { status: "DRAFT" }", locations: [{line: 23, column: 19}],…}
3
: 
{message: "String cannot represent value: { status: "COMPLETED" }",…}
4
: 
{,…}

